(62306, 178942, 0, 0, '序曲  Overture', '在這繁忙的社會中，人們好像漫無目的的隨著時間的消逝而行走著。大家似乎彷彿期待著一種矚光，能夠給予我們方向與未來。然而，大家似乎好像不知道，這光其實離我們並不遙遠。', '2013-04-07 00:00:00', 2013, 19, 1, 4, '', '', 85, '', '陳恩光', '陳恩光', '陳恩光Nicolas Chen', 'K-Gospel Music', '', 0, 0, 0, '2013-04-01 15:36:35', '2015-03-12 14:00:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(62307, 178942, 5722, 2, 'You''re All I Need ', '不管高山或是低谷，那位愛我們耶穌，是我們一生的依靠。我們的一切所需，祂都知道。你的心情，祂都明瞭。\n\n演唱：Sylvie Cheng\n吉他：林旻億\nBass：潘秋安\nKeyboard：司安迪\n鼓：陳恩光', '2013-04-07 00:00:00', 2013, 19, 1, 4, '走在黑暗幽谷 看似一團迷霧\n當我無助害怕的時候\n你就像光和雲 帶領我前面路\n指引我人生的方向\n\n我歌唱一切是為了你\n我讚美將榮耀歸與你\n\n我要唱  大聲唱\n向你唱出新歌是為了敬拜你\n我敬拜你\n因你是主 我的王\n是我一生中唯一所倚靠\nYou’re all I need.\n\n在你沒有難成事  靠祢恩典我能站立\n從今時直到永遠  你的慈愛永遠長存', '', 256, '', '陳恩光', '陳恩光', '陳恩光Nicolas Chen', 'K-Gospel Music', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-04-01 15:37:09', '2015-03-12 14:00:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(62308, 178942, 5722, 3, '對話 Conversation', '我們常常都試圖的想抓住甚麼，想了解甚麼，但是卻又無功而返，常常自己在自己的世界裡打轉。直到遇見了祢，從此不再迷網。\n\n演唱：Sylvie Cheng\n吉他：林旻億\nbass：潘秋安\nkeyboard：司安迪\n鼓：陳恩光', '2013-04-07 00:00:00', 2013, 19, 1, 4, '生命的意義到底是甚麼\n有甚麼精彩的\n我不去問不去想\n把它拋得遠遠的\n周圍的一切 就像鋼琴鍵\n跳躍著動人旋律\n不論大雨無論天晴\n出發一個人的旅行\n\n手裡的相機從沒停過\n模糊的焦點回憶 盤旋在黑暗洞口\n這一瞬間\n彷彿一切都將停止運作\n\n你我會相遇是巧合意外\n你我的遭遇使內心澎湃\n慢慢的靠近了 使我有了希望\n你我會相遇是巧合意外\n你我的相遇使內心澎湃\n那些回憶 眷戀過去的迷惘 \n就隨風飄蕩', '', 248, '', '陳恩光', '陳恩光、安綺', '陳恩光Nicolas Chen', 'K-Gospel Music', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-04-01 15:37:59', '2015-03-12 14:00:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(62309, 178942, 0, 0, 'Jesus', '這位耶穌，在我的心裡面到底能夠改變我甚麼？祂又是誰？', '2013-04-07 00:00:00', 2013, 19, 1, 4, 'yo I got something to say\nif you don''t know who Jesus is\nI got news, man\n1.\nI wanna be\nwith Jesus for the rest of my life\nopen book of Proverbs\nmake wisdom my wife\nwanna raise my hands in a room of believers\nscream ''til my lungs explode on the receivers\nhigh on the spirit\ndrunk on his wine\nGod loves to party\nhave a good time\nif you''re not on the list\nthen you''re uninvited\nthat includes Satan,\nand the crew that he rides with\n2.\nyou gotta have faith like a child\nto hang out with Jesus\nyou ain''t a policeman\nwhat is a christian?\nsomebody who listens\nto Jesus'' voice\nloves to be with him\nit''s not about doing good deeds\ntrying not to fall off your man-made walls\nit ain''t hard to swallow\nlove Him first\neverything else''ll follow\n3.\nyou gotta have faith like a child\nto hang out with Jesus\nyou ain''t a policeman\nwhat is a christian?\nsomebody who listens\nto Jesus'' voice\nloves to be with him\nit''s not about doing good deeds\ntrying not to fall off your man-made walls\nit ain''t hard to swallow\nlove Him first\neverything else''ll follow\n4.\nto those who tip-toe\nthrough life on a tight rope\nlife ain''t a sideshow\nit''s about loving God first in the morning\nhanging out with Him all day''s not boring\nif you want meaning as your weeks go\ndrink up His words\nlearn to love people\nno love is greater than this\ngiving up your life for your neighbor''s legit\n5.\nmake sure whatever you say is\nrooted in his word\ndon''t drive on the curb\notherwise your wheels''ll explode\nyour life is on hold\nwhile you bandage your woes\nit ain''t about rules and regulations\ntry to emulate Him\ntaste Him embrace Him\nwide is the road to destruction\nnarrow be the one that leads to the Son\n6.\ntake off your glasses\ntime to buy a new pair\nhell isn''t fun there''s nothing to do there\nheaven parties hard to eternity\nno room for darkness to burde